### GET - Obtener todos los gerentes
GET http://127.0.0.1:5000/gerente HTTP/1.1 
Content-Type: application/json

###

### POST - Crear un nuevo gerente
POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/gerente HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre": "Juan Pérez"
}

###

### GET - Obtener gerente por ID
GET http://127.0.0.1:5000/gerente/1 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

###

### PUT - Actualizar gerente
PUT http://127.0.0.1:5000/gerente HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 1,
  "nombre": "Carlos García",
  "tienda": "Tienda Principal"
}

###

### DELETE - Eliminar gerente
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:5000/gerente/1 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json